evidence.title: New Shoes
evidence.text: "New Shoes" is a song by Scottish singer-songwriter Paolo Nutini, released as the fourth single from debut album, These Streets. It was used as the headlining single for the US release of the album. The song peaked at number 21 on the UK Singles Chart, number eight on the US Billboard Bubbling Under Hot 100 chart, and number one on the Billboard Triple A chart. The song was used for a 2007 international ad campaign by Puma AG.
